  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to Evolution</title>

    <para>
      The <application>Evolution</application> package contains an
      integrated mail, calendar and address book suite designed for the
      <application>GNOME</application> environment.
    </para>

    &lfs121_checked;

